		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 3px;
		height: 100%;
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.site-card-inner {
		position: relative;
		padding: 16px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 14px;
		width: 100%;
	}

